---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <main class="content-container">
        <h1 class="font-bold text-6 my-4">Popular Webdev Tools</h1>

        <p>
            These are tools that I made for myself and decided to share with others because these are commonly needed by
            web developers.
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li class="mb-3">
                <a href="/tools/base64-encode.html">Base64 Encoder</a>
                <p>
                    A simple online base64 encoder that is compatible with the base64 command line tool shipped on most
                    linux/unix systems.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="mb-3">
                <a href="/tools/base64-decode.html">Base64 Decoder</a>
                <p>A simple online base64 decoder that also supports URL-safe encoded texts.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="mb-3">
                <a href="/tools/json-beautifier.html">JSON beautifier</a>
                <p>This tool makes any JSON pretty.</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </main>
</Layout>
